{"tid":2166552,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"27間零僱員公司獲政府「保就業」計劃資助，合共獲取125萬元","createTime":"2020-08-20T13:20:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T13:20:47.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d2455ef75b00d313229a0ddcc8f65f348c462f15","tid":2166552,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T13:20:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1544935-20200820.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1544935-20200820.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=hRZI3RxrLdWDWG%2FiPctn5WZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=79d4b913\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1544935-20200820.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=2c8f8c83\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1544935-20200820.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n政府公布「保就業」計劃新一批獲資助的僱主名單，當中有27間公司承諾受薪人數為零，合共獲取125萬元補貼。<br />\n<br />\n27間零僱員公司獲取的補貼介乎675元至36萬元不等，獲發36萬元補貼的公司是惠富企業有限公司。<br />\n<br />\n新一批獲資助的企業，合共領取政府超過28億元補貼，涉及僱員人數超過12萬人。"}]}